app.entity_classes

Class MenuItems

  • java.lang.Object
    • app.entity_classes.MenuItems

  • public class MenuItems
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a menu item in a restaurant or food service application.

    This class encapsulates the properties of a menu item, such as its ID, name, availability, price, and category. Additional properties like description and image can be included if needed.
